\end{array}} \right|$<br>$=\hat{i} \sqrt{3}(2.5-2)-\hat{j}(7.5-8)+\hat{k}(3-4) \sqrt{3}$<br>$=0.5 \sqrt{3} \hat{i}+0.5 \hat{j}-\sqrt{3} \hat{k}$<br>Unit vector along $(\vec{P} \times \vec{Q})$ is given by<br>$\hat{n}=\dfrac{(\vec{P} \times \vec{Q})}{|\vec{P} \times \vec{Q}|}$<br>$\hat{n}=\dfrac{0.5 \sqrt{3} \hat{i}+0.5 \hat{j}-\sqrt{3} \hat{k}}{\left.[0.5 \sqrt{3})^{2}+0.5^{2}+3\right]^{1 / 2}}$<br>$=\dfrac{\dfrac{1}{2}(\sqrt{3} \hat{i}+\hat{j}-2 \sqrt{3} \hat{k})}{2}$<br>So, $x=4$

